annotationA: Rhomboid-like protein; Roughoid (Ru) is an intra-membrane serine protease localized in the endoplasmic reticulum. Ru processes EGFR ligands in specific tissues, most notably the eye
annotationB: Exocyst complex component 7; Required for exocytosis. Thought to function in intracellular vesicle targeting and docking before SNARE complex formation
